settings.description: what's up with all these spinning spiny shells? well... be glad ya aren't playing the NES and SNES version here, for ya can't stomp them in them versions of SMB3, but here? you can!

so much sand, with so many coins found deep under such! think you can unearth enough for a nice three extra lives?
don't forget to check what's in the bricks as well!
